  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's a funny story that here is my partner that used to schlep with me the-- the--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--bricks.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I could never remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then she one time we met here in a store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had a store in [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Fins. ?] And she says to me, now I must tell you this story.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, what story will you tell me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you remember when we were partners in schlepping the bricks?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were always the first one in front, and I was in the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, I don't know, I never thought about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, I'll tell you why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when he used to let the-- the dogs down on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So whenever he felt like to make a show, he-- you should be the first one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was hysterical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was hysterical.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She told-- told this as a joke.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Believe me, I know that she-- at that time even didn't cross her mind that it could something happen like this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But now, when we came here, and when we met, there was one time in her store she says to me, you never thought about it, why you were always in the front and I in the back?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You told me earlier today that when the Germans came in, your father's wife wanted to sell you to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is a different story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is already after the slaughter when we survived on design of my-- we were at that time, her-- my stepmother's two sisters and mother lived with us when we were placed, I told you, across the army barracks, and when slowly, slowly they started to form a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But before they formed the ghetto they made a [NON-ENGLISH], a slaughter, the first time.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
